    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，边缘节点作为数据入口。那它采集的数据往哪里送？是直连云端还是先经过本地聚合？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先经过MQTT Broker。工业场景里网络不稳定，用Broker做缓冲和协议转换更可靠。边缘节点把数据推送给Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以是边缘节点指向Broker的数据流向。我理解为单向推送，不需要Broker回传控制指令对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，方向反了。应该是Broker订阅边缘节点的主题，但画图时箭头表示数据从边缘节点发出，指向Broker。你刚才说的\"指向\"是对的，我怕你画成Broker指向边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "清楚了，箭头从边缘节点指向MQTT Broker，表示数据上报方向。我这就把这两个节点和连线画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "画好了。边缘节点在左，MQTT Broker在右，带箭头的连线表示数据流。您看下这个结构符合工业现场的部署逻辑吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
